text: Reg Strikes Back is the 21st studio album by Elton John and was released on 24 June 1988. It went to top 20 in Australia, Austria, Canada, Denmark, Germany, Italy, the Netherlands, Norway, Sweden, Switzerland, the United Kingdom and the United States. == Track listing == * Sides one and two were combined as tracks 1â€“10 on CD reissues.
